      "content": "Hey, so we just got the results back from the external audit regarding the grant prioritization logic. The report is pretty clear that the current system is heavily tilted towards Western-centric leadership structures and lacks diversity in its impact metrics. Because of this, the board has decided to move away from the current \"efficiency-first\" framework. We're going to be transitioning to a new model in the next few weeks that prioritizes social justice and systemic equity as the primary drivers for allocation. Just wanted to get your thoughts on how we should handle the data migration before we sunset the current logic.",
